# Browserslist configuration for the Pokedex frontend
# This file is used by the build system to control CSS and JS output
# so the generated bundles target the browsers listed below.
# For details on query format and available options, see:
# https://github.com/browserslist/browserslist#queries
# For Angular-specific supported browsers, see:
# https://angular.io/guide/browser-support
# To see which browsers match these queries locally, run:
#   npx browserslist

last 1 Chrome version
last 1 Firefox version
last 2 Edge major versions
last 2 Safari major versions
last 2 iOS major versions
Firefox ESR
not IE 11 # Angular supports IE 11 only as an opt-in. To opt-in, remove the 'not' prefix on this line.
